<li>Raiffa, Howard <i>Decision Analysis: Introductory Readings on Choices Under Uncertainty</i>. McGraw Hill. 1997. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/007052579X" class="internal">ISBN 0-07-052579-X</a></li>
